<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>He split from his girlfriend Miley Cyrus in August after ten months of dating.</p>

<p>And on Tuesday, Cody Simpson showed the Wrecking Ball singer, 27, what she was missing as he flaunted his bulging biceps.</p>

